name: iWedding Invitation ordering, discount information & delivery upgrades
description:
For a delivery upgrade please select an option from the drop down box. For information on wedding invitations please read on...


To order wedding invitations in your favourite Rosie Wonders design with your personalised details printed inside just pop the number of invites you need in your basket and proceed to checkout...

discounts are offered for orders over 50 (15%), 80 (20%) and 120 (30%) invites. Depending on how many you order, please use the following codes,
WEDDING50, WEDDING80 or WEDDING120.

Then email your EXACT wording to rosie@rosiewonders.co.uk along with your choice of font. Typewriter or Twirly. In black or pink.

Invitations are printed with the Rosie Wonders logo on the back. If you would like your names printed on the back please request this in your email.

For orders of more than 50 invitations please purchase a £3 Special Delivery upgrade. For orders of over 100 cards please purchase a £5 courier upgrade from the drop down box.

Please allow a least 14 days for delivery.

For samples or queries please call the studio. We would love to hear from you! +44 (0)207 241 2909
